---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="rlayout animate-on-load">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>GitHub Pages Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      This website is hosted using <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>. GitHub may
      collect User Personal Information, including logs of visitor IP addresses,
      to comply with legal obligations and to maintain the security and
      integrity of the site. See the <a
        href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Privacy Statement</a
      > for more details.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>
      This website does not use any analytics or tracking mechanisms. We do not
      monitor user behavior or collect personal data. You can browse the site
      anonymously.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and LocalStorage</h2>
    <p>This website does not use cookies.</p>
    <p>
      However, we use <code>localStorage</code> to remember your consent for loading
      third-party comments via Giscus. This is stored only in your browser and is
      never transmitted to any server.
    </p>

    <h2>Comments via Giscus</h2>
    <p>
      Commenting functionality is powered by <a
        href="https://giscus.app"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Giscus</a
      >, which integrates with GitHub Discussions. When you choose to load
      comments, Giscus may load scripts from GitHub and process data according
      to GitHub's privacy practices.
    </p>
    <p>
      To post a comment, you will need to sign in with your GitHub account. When
      you comment, your public GitHub profile (including your username and
      avatar) will be visible to others. We do not have access to or store any
      of this data.
    </p>
    <p>
      By clicking “Load Comments,” you consent to loading third-party content.
      For more information, see the <a
        href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Privacy Policy</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>External Links</h2>
    <p>
      This website may link to third-party services such as GitHub. We are not
      responsible for the content or privacy practices of those services. Please
      review their privacy policies separately.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to open an issue at <a
        href="https://github.com/xyroton/xyroton.github.io/issues"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">our GitHub repository</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    margin-bottom: -0.6rem;
  }
  a {
    color: var(--secondary);
  }
</style>
